Jainism is considered an eternal teaching with the tirthankaras guiding all time cycles in cosmology.

But the city’s crown court was told he was selling the wraps, with 59 per cent purity cocaine, at £40 each to clear debts after getting addicted as a teenager.

It is known as the festival of lights, but it also signifies the triumph of good over evil, the celebration of light over darkness, and belief in knowledge over ignorance. Diwali is the celebration of empowerment to do good so that it can bring joy, prosperity, and wealth to all. People worldwide light rows of diyas (oil lamps) and cover their homes in lights to celebrate this festival of hope and new beginnings.
